Title: White Whale
Writer: Daniel J. Goor (created by), Michael Schur (created by), Matt Lawton, Carol Kolb, Carly Hallam (executive story editor), Jessica Polonsky (story editor)
Actors: Andy Samberg, Stephanie Beatriz, Terry Crews, Melissa Fumero
Plot: Rosa and Amy track down a killer who's managed to elude them for seven years; Terry helps Jake with his wedding chores; Holt and his rival try to convince each other to resign from the campaign for Commissioner.
